I can't reach him.
I'm worried.

5
00:00:09,977 --> 00:00:11,946
Here they come.

6
00:00:16,050 --> 00:00:18,719
- Make way!
- Make way.

7
00:00:19,353 --> 00:00:23,324
Tonight at 9:00 P.M. in Mitaka
City, Nakano-Suginami districts,

8
00:00:23,424 --> 00:00:26,527
police arrested the 29-year old
manager of a red-light bar

9
00:00:26,660 --> 00:00:29,630
based on reports of threatening
and blackmailing customers;

10
00:00:29,764 --> 00:00:33,768
disturbing the peace with
intimidating customer-barking;

11
00:00:33,901 --> 00:00:37,505
alleged criminal activities of
fraud and extortion;

12
00:00:37,638 --> 00:00:40,107
along with two cronies associated
with the red-light establishment,

13
00:00:40,241 --> 00:00:42,910
