obstruction of public duties.

14
00:00:43,010 --> 00:00:45,980
What? The immigration bureau?

15
00:00:46,213 --> 00:00:48,616
Who is this Yuka?

16
00:00:48,716 --> 00:00:49,517
Huh?

17
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:51,452
You mean Bin Rin?

18
00:00:52,453 --> 00:00:54,188
Fu Bin Rin.

19
00:00:54,422 --> 00:00:56,857
It's uncertain if
this is even her real name.

20
00:00:56,991 --> 00:00:57,858
Tourist visa.

21
00:00:57,992 --> 00:00:59,260
It's expired.

22
00:00:59,393 --> 00:01:01,495
She also gave birth, didn't she?

23
